transcript:
hey there just wanted to check up on you
I know it's been tough recently with all
the work piling up keeping it
financially I just want to remind you
that it's okay to cry or feel
overwhelmed it happens to everyone
you just have to remember to push
through these times think about all the
good times you've had spending time with
family and friends doing the hobbies
that you enjoy most
but if you ever need to shed some tears
that's okay just know someone will be
there to comfort you during these times
whether it's your lover family or close
friend you are never alone
feeling down I'll never be a problem
because everything will be just fine
